    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>vaXinator</i> puts you in the microscopic shoes of the <strong>last White Blood Cell</strong>, on a mission to protect the body from a relentless invasion of pathogens. Your goal? <strong>Fend off diseases</strong> and keep the body alive!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3214380/extras/8a9dd4e8e0edc23fada9db1222cdfa0b.avif?t=1731605498\" width=600 height=82 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Two Game Modes:</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Easy Mode:</strong> For a more relaxed experience.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Fever Mode:</strong> For those seeking a true test of skill. Think you can survive the heat?</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Global Leaderboards:</strong> <br>Compete against players worldwide! See how long you can survive and climb to the top in both game modes.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3214380/extras/ae0f77c04269c782f6c7a17c54a612a1.avif?t=1731605498\" width=600 height=82 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Paracetamol Shield:</strong> <br>Protect yourself from damage for a limited time and fend off enemy attacks.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Antibody Booster:</strong> <br>Supercharge your firepower! Increase your shooting speed and unleash a barrage of bullets.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3214380/extras/c79e4201eac3c6b5ef77a317d7632675.avif?t=1731605498\" width=600 height=82 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Wave-Based Combat:</strong> <br>Fight through <strong>endless waves of enemies</strong> with unique attacks and behaviors. Your objective is simple: <strong>survive as long as possible</strong> and rack up points!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Can you hold the line and save the body from infection? Play <i>vaXinator</i> and prove your skills in this action-packed roguelike!</p>",
